song.title: Zelda5 Mix
song.info:
Hello there. Yet another track from skyline/ Dragoon-kun. This is one of my personal favorites...
Seeing how many songs were made for the FF series, I decided to do the Zelda series some justice. I plan on making a lot more in the near future. I hope that the tracking I've done lately has improved my style. Until then, enjoy this song!
Best listened to with a KOSS headset along with IT 2.14.
